-/*
- *  RFC 1115/1319 compliant MD2 implementation
- *  The MD2 algorithm was designed by Ron Rivest in 1989.
- *
- *  http://www.ietf.org/rfc/rfc1115.txt
- *  http://www.ietf.org/rfc/rfc1319.txt
- */
